--VALUES--('26', '4.95858E+15', '北京外语广播', '2023-10-19 15:33', '中巴经济走廊是中国和巴基斯坦共建“一带一路”的标志性项目。它于2013年启动建设，今年整整十个年头。来自巴基斯坦独立新闻社的记者穆罕默德•扎米尔•阿萨迪表示中巴经济走廊给巴基斯坦带来了巨大的变化。#我见“一带一路”# The China-Pakistan Economic Corridor (CPEC) is one of the landmark projects between China and Pakistan under the Belt and Road Initiative. It started construction in 2013 and this year marks the 10th anniversary. Muhammad Zamir Assadi, reporter of the Independent News Pakistan, said the CPEC has brought great changes to Pakistan. 北京外语广播的微博视频', '0', '0', '0', '409', '42.2万', 'f', '', '', '北京', '中国')
